{"tid":590841,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"起動九龍東- 啟德發展計劃","createTime":"2018-03-13T04:02:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-13T04:11:02.000Z","uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"af02148b7001453def112ac77841095ec3510df1","tid":590841,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T04:02:56.000Z","msg":"啟德（英語：Kai Tak）又稱啟德發展區（英語：Kai Tak Development Area，簡稱KTDA），或依地理稱為東南九龍（英語：South East Kowloon），是香港地方，位於九龍東南部。現時根據香港政府「分區計劃大綱圖」，包括的是原啟德機場用地，以及鄰近海旁；西至海心公園，東至茶果嶺海濱區[1]。<br />\n<br />\n啟德現時正在根據《啟德發展計劃》和《起動九龍東》進行新一輪的發展。"},{"pid":"5eba47de4dee6b45bfe1128caa89df1502b5dadf","tid":590841,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T04:11:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/13/121055_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F13%2F121055_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=9e4944e5&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}